Accepts values of "first" and "visited". All other values are ignored. "first" adds the following constraint: true only if the currentTiddler has ''not'' been visited. Equivalent to `before="[<currentTiddler>]"`. "visited" is the opposite: true only if currentTiddler ''has'' been visited already. Equivalent to `after="[<currentTiddler>]"`. The <<wlink FirstWidget>> and <<wlink VisitedWidget>> are shorthands for this.